WEBVTT

00:01.678 --> 00:03.211
<i>Previously on "Zero Hour"...</i>

00:04.711 --> 00:06.649
They're breaking in.

00:06.683 --> 00:08.116
We know who might have her.

00:08.151 --> 00:10.018
He's the highest end mercenary
in the world.

00:10.053 --> 00:12.821
It's about a clock. 1938.
The church appointed

00:12.855 --> 00:14.089
12 new apostles.

00:14.123 --> 00:16.358
They call themselves
The Shepherds.

00:16.393 --> 00:20.261
Their mission is to protect
the holiest of relics.

00:20.296 --> 00:22.630
Who are they protecting from?

00:22.665 --> 00:24.532
Tell her just a matter of time

00:24.567 --> 00:26.467
till she has the object
she seeks.

00:26.502 --> 00:27.969
I have the first three clocks.

00:29.505 --> 00:32.941
Vincent has never kept
a hostage alive, so why Laila?

00:32.975 --> 00:35.943
We did it.

00:35.977 --> 00:37.344
- Where is she?
- What are you doing

00:37.378 --> 00:38.445
my husband's flight...

00:38.479 --> 00:40.214
one passenger was supposed
to be on it.

00:40.248 --> 00:43.317
- What does that have to do with Laila?
- She lied!

00:43.351 --> 00:44.985
The clocks... where are they?

00:48.770 --> 00:51.524
<font color="#3399FF">Zero Hour 01x05</font>
<font color=#00ff00>Suspension</font>

00:51.644 --> 00:53.808
==sync, correction by <font color=#00ff00>dcdah</font>==
for www.addic7ed.com

00:53.928 --> 00:57.630
<i>4 is the number of seasons,</i>

00:57.664 --> 01:00.366
<i>the phases of the earth.</i>

01:00.400 --> 01:07.340
<i>Life comes full cycle...</i>
<i>First death, then birth.</i>

01:10.343 --> 01:13.578
Mankind once feared
the locust.

01:13.579 --> 01:16.248
He believed they were
the hand of God,

01:16.282 --> 01:20.018
decimating crops
to punish our sins.

01:20.053 --> 01:23.421
But then we learned
we can't control sin

01:23.456 --> 01:25.156
or Grace,

01:25.190 --> 01:28.592
but we <i>can</i> control science.

01:28.627 --> 01:31.528
Today, science destroys
the locust,

01:31.563 --> 01:33.397
crops thrive,

01:33.431 --> 01:35.066
and now...

01:35.100 --> 01:38.335
God's power resides
in the hand of man,

01:38.370 --> 01:42.372
so we must <i>use</i> that power.

01:49.747 --> 01:51.815
I'm glad you understand.

01:53.885 --> 01:55.851
Now what did you hear
from White Vincent?

01:55.886 --> 01:57.386
Has he found the clock?

01:59.000 --> 02:05.074
Advertise your product or brand here
